beer.beer_description:
The Strata hop delivers an aromatic array of pulpy orange meets grapefruit, with mango jam, layered upon a base of tropical passion fruit and citrus undertones. There is a lingering dank & herbaceous dimension which finishes through with a full-length bitterness and pleasant alcohol sweetness. A beer to match our artwork. 

This Double IPA is the epitome of our Unbridled Unicorn
